window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Unseen Fleets Come and Worlds Burn</b>&nbsp;</p> <p>The Unliving are implacable. Unreasonable. No one knows what they want, beyond souls, and bone for their war machines and ships. Now they've set their sights on the Inurans, and hey, I couldn't wish an army of necromancers on a better target.&nbsp;</p> <p>There's just one problem.&nbsp;</p> <p>I'm trapped on the Inuran Trade Moon, and the necromancers are attacking. Even if I can get the minister back to her ship we'll still need to find a way to fight their flagship. That's going to be tough to do without enough magic to power the Word of Xal.&nbsp;</p> <p>If I pull it off I think I get a bonus though. Also, there's that living thing.</p>"; 
